{"word":"παραβαίνω","slug":"παραβαίνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>παραβαίνω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:παρά\">παρά</a>, βαίνω</el> ‘walk’; ‘bypass’] ‘divert from the path’, in imagery<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp> divert</b> <el>ἀφ</el>’ <el>ἧς παρέβη <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:Ἰούδας\">Ἰούδας</a></el> which Judas bypassed <b><a href='B:510 1:25'>Ac 1:25</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp> overstep, violate <a href='B:470 15:2'>Mt 15:2f</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:παρά\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:παραβάλλω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}